content: The link for this file already exists with the Editing permission. Change the access rights to Filling?

comment.text: This translation key is used to display a message that prompts users to change the access rights of an existing link from Editing permission to Filling. It appears in a modal dialog when editing a file and is triggered by clicking "Submit".

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation of 'Filling' is not accurate. 'Filling' in this context refers to a permission level allowing users to only fill in existing content, not the act of filling something.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: الرابط الخاص بهذا الملف موجود بالفعل مع صلاحية التحرير. هل تريد تغيير حقوق الوصول إلى "الإكمال"؟

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While technically correct, the Arabic sentence structure could be slightly improved for better flow and naturalness.  It sounds a little literal from the English.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: الرابط الخاص بهذا الملف موجود بالفعل مع صلاحية التحرير. هل ترغب في تغيير حقوق الوصول إلى "الإكمال"؟

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation of "access rights" is not accurate. "İnzibati hüquqları" translates to administrative rights, not access rights.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Bu fayl üçün olan link artıq redaktə imkanı ilə mövcuddur. Baxış imkanlarına dəyişdirsiniz?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'Filling' is translated to 'doldurmağa' which doesn't accurately represent the intended meaning of 'view only' or 'filling in'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Bu fayl üçün olan link artıq redaktə imkanı ilə mövcuddur. Baxış imkanlarına dəyişdirsiniz?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation of "Filling" is not the most natural or accurate representation of its meaning in this context. "Filling" implies adding information, whereas the original English implies a level of access (view-only, similar to 'viewing' or 'completing').
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Връзката към този файл вече съществува с разрешение за редактиране. Искате ли да промените правата за достъп до четене?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation of 'Filling' is not idiomatic. 'Filling' in this context refers to allowing users to only fill in fields, not a literal filling action. A more appropriate translation would convey the idea of 'view only' or 'commenting'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Le lien pour ce fichier existe déjà avec le droit d'édition. Voulez-vous modifier les droits d'accès en lecture seule/commentaire ?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The French translation uses a question mark at the end of the sentence which indicates a direct question. The English phrasing is more of a statement followed by a question about changing rights. While not strictly incorrect, changing the punctuation would align the style.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Le lien pour ce fichier existe déjà avec le droit d'édition. Modifier les droits d'accès en remplissage.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase "Փոխե՞լ մուտքի իրավունքները" is a direct translation of "Change the access rights" but sounds slightly unnatural in Armenian. A more natural phrasing would be something like "Սրան ի՞նչ կարգավիճակ ունենք" or "Արդյոք ցանկալիք է փոփոխել կարգավիճակը" .
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Արդյոք ցանկալիք է փոփոխել կարգավիճակը Լրացնելու թույլտվությամբ:

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The English phrase 'Filling' doesn't have a direct equivalent in Korean that accurately conveys the intended meaning of 'Filling' in the context of access rights. 'Filling' refers to the ability to only fill in forms/fields, not actively editing. The Korean translation '작성' (jakseong) generally means 'writing' or 'creation,' which is closer to the concept of 'writing' content rather than simply filling in existing fields.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: 이 파일 링크는 이미 편집 권한으로 존재합니다. 작성 권한으로 제한하시겠습니까?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation of 'Filling' is not accurate. 'Filling' in this context likely refers to 'view-only' access or the ability to add data without editing the underlying structure. A more accurate translation would convey that meaning.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ລິ້ງສໍາລັບໄຟລ໌ນີ້ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວດ້ວຍສິດການແກ້ໄຂ ປ່ຽນສິດການເຂົ້າເຖິງເປັນການເບິ່ງຢ່າງດຽວ ຫຼື ເພື່ອຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນເທົ່ານັ້ນບໍ?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The question mark at the end of the Lao translation is somewhat abrupt. A smoother phrasing might improve readability.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: ລິ້ງສໍາລັບໄຟລ໌ນີ້ມີຢູ່ແລ້ວດ້ວຍສິດການແກ້ໄຂ ປ່ຽນສິດການເຂົ້າເຖິງເປັນການຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນບໍ?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'with the Editing permission' is not accurately translated. 'Rediģēšanas atļauja' translates literally to 'Editing permission' which sounds unnatural in Latvian. A more natural phrasing would be something like 'ar rediģēšanas tiesībām' or 'ir rediģēšana'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Faila saite jau pastāv ar rediģēšanas tiesībām. Vai mainīt piekļuves tiesības uz aizpildīšanu?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While not strictly incorrect, the sentence structure can be improved for better flow in Latvian. The addition of 'ir' (is) before 'rediģēšana' can make the sentence smoother. While not essential, it is a common usage in this context.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Faila saite jau pastāv un ir rediģēšana. Vai mainīt piekļuves tiesības uz aizpildīšanu?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation 'Link-ul către acest fișier cu permisiunea de editare deja existent' is not a natural phrasing in Romanian. It translates literally but doesn't read well.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Un link pentru acest fișier există deja cu permisiunea de editare.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation of 'Filling' as 'Completare' is technically correct but might be confusing to the end user. 'Filling' in this context refers to adding content to a file, not completing something.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Permisiunea de acces la completare (adăugare conținut)?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The sentence 'Link-ul către acest fișier cu permisiunea de editare deja existent' contains a grammatical error. The adjective 'existent' should be placed differently.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Link-ul către acest fișier există deja cu permisiunea de editare.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The question mark is not at the end of the complete sentence. It's attached to 'Completare' which is part of a clause. There is an unidiomatic reading of the whole sentence.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Un link pentru acest fișier există deja cu permisiunea de editare. Doriți să modificați permisiunea de acces la completare (adăugare conținut)?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase 'Change the access rights to Filling?' is not accurately translated. 'Filling' in this context likely refers to a permission level allowing users to fill out forms or data within the file. The Sinhala translation 'ප්‍රවිණිවාස අයිතිවාසිකම් පුරවා දැමීම සඳහා වෙනස් කරන්න?' is too literal and doesn't convey the intended meaning of changing permissions to a 'filling' or data entry level. A more accurate translation would describe the new permission level.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: මෙම ෆයිල සඳහා වූ සබැඳිය දැනටමත් සංपादन අවසරයකින් පවතී. දත්ත ඇතුළත් කිරීමේ අවසරයකට වෙනස් කරන්න? (This translates to: 'The link for this file already exists with the Editing permission. Change it to a Data Entry permission?')

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'සබැඳිය' (sabandiya) is used for 'link'. While correct, a more common and potentially clearer term in this context might be 'ලේඛනයා' (lekhaayaa) or similar, depending on the specific terminology used within the application.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: මෙම ෆයිල සඳහා වූ ලේඛනයා දැනටමත් සංपादन අවසරයකින් පවතී. (This translates to: 'The link for this file already exists with the Editing permission.')

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase "Izpolnjevanje?" doesn't accurately convey the meaning of "Filling" in the context of access rights. "Filling" here refers to a permission level, typically implying 'view-only' or 'fillable'. A more appropriate term would be something along the lines of 'Dopolnjevanje' or 'Ogledovanje' depending on the precise nuance required.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider using 'Dopolnjevanje?' or 'Ogledovanje?' for a more accurate translation of 'Filling'.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The question mark at the end of the Slovenian sentence feels slightly abrupt and could benefit from a softer transition. While grammatically correct, it's worth considering a more conversational tone.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Consider adding a connective phrase before the question mark, e.g., 'Spremeniti pravice dostopa na Dopolnjevanje, želite?' or similar.

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The term "Веза" (Veza) translates to 'Link' but in this context, 'connection' or 'association' might be more natural in Serbian. 'Veza' can sometimes imply a personal relationship, which is not the intended meaning.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Узбуна за ову датотеку већ постоји са дозволом за уређивање. Да ли желите да промените права приступа на попуњавање?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The phrase "права приступа" (prava pristupa) is grammatically correct but sounds slightly formal. A more natural phrasing in this context would be "права приступа" or “доступа”).
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Узбуна за ову датотеку већ постоји са дозволом за уређивање. Да ли желите да промените доступ на попуњавање?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The word 'datoteku' (file) is technically correct, but 'datotečni fajl' or just 'fajl' would be more common and natural in this context. While 'datoteku' isn't wrong, it sounds slightly formal and less user-friendly.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Veza za ovaj fajl već postoji sa dozvolom za uređivanje. Da li želite da promenite prava pristupa na popunjavanje?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: While not incorrect, a more conversational tone might be achieved by rephrasing the question. Consider a softer approach.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Veza za ovaj fajl već postoji sa dozvolom za uređivanje. Želite li promeniti prava pristupa na popunjavanje?

ai_spell_check_issues.description: The translation of 'Filling' is not accurate. 'Filling' in this context refers to the ability to only fill in fields, not the act of filling something. A more appropriate term would be 'yalnızca doldurma' or 'sadece doldurma'.
ai_spell_check_issues.suggestion: Bu dosyanın bağlantısı zaten Düzenleme izniyle mevcut. Erişim haklarını yalnızca doldurma olarak değiştirmek ister misiniz?
